= Forgot Password

== 1. Forgot Password Request

Request a forgot password email that contains a deep link to mobile app or fallback link to reset the user's password.
The fallback link is `<front_url>/forgot-password/<token>`. The data associated with the deep link available to mobile apps:

[source]
[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`email` | `string` | The request email address.
|`token` | `string` |
|`$fallback_url` | `string` | Link to react app to handle request. Maybe link:https://dev.branch.io/getting-started/configuring-links/guide/#fallback-url-customization[platform specific]
|`type` | `string` | Type of request. Set to `forgot-password`.
|===

[source]
----
POST /forgot-password
----

=== Input

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`email` | `string` | **Required**  The email address on the user's account.
|===

== 2. Reset Password

Reset the user's password using the token.

[source]
----
POST /forgot-password/reset
----

=== Input

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`token` | `string` | **Required**
|`new_password` | `string` | **Required**
|===


